And I make content that doesn't need to be brand new for it to be relevant.

114
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:11,520
How do you really get views on YouTube?

115
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:14,319
How do you make great videos that get millions of views?

116
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:20,240
