118
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:33,520
So something like that where you have an age that people can relate to big number like 10 sources of income people like wo and then a dollar amount just really makes them curious to click on it.

119
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,600
Those types of titles have done really well for me.

120
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:39,600
So a huge part of my channel is evergreen SEO content.

121
