130
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:09,360
And then in the actual video itself, we had a lot of storytelling.

131
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:13,199
So that's really how you get people to click on it and then actually watch the entire video.

132
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:13,440
Yeah.

