174
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:28,240
A full-time person for most positions, I'd say, is about $600 to $1,000 per month.

175
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:33,600
you have these successful YouTube channels and now you're starting a little bit of a different business uh with your staffing firm.

